Login application using spring mvc

Database with users table
CREATE TABLE users
( name varchar2(50) NOT NULL,
  password varchar2(50)
);
insert into users values ('admin','admin');

DB query uses Uses queryForObject - It is a JDBC Statement, not a PreparedStatement

